Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.71,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.38,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:43.89,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel like I was just having \Na really important dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.19,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's going to bother me all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:57.03,Title,D,0000,0000,0000,,A Midsummer Night's Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:55.84,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,And summer break starts tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:32.96,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he quit the track team \Nto focus on his studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Has he picked up any bad habits, \Nlike staying out late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:43.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I think there has to be some reason \Nwhy his grades have fallen so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:48.59,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to say that I spent the \Nwhole time playing in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.49,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.77,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.46,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I'd said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.24,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... But when did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:05.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You have to start thinking about \Nwhat you'll do after high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any dreams or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Like following in your father's footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.96,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,His father has nothing to do with his future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.32,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:25.13,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's something wrong \Nwith me, with the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:31.39,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,But most likely, I'm only imagining it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:35.52,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm actually just trying to escape\N because I don't feel like studying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.14,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,the stuff they assign at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.73,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Amara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.00,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're working?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My family owns this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.23,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to come unannounced?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:01.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. My parents aren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:04.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.89,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Daichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I found him at the arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:12.01,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Moco and Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.21,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at piloting robots, Daichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.66,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:34.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Piloting robots...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.67,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.45,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's invite Daichi-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, I'm sure Ai will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Having lots of people will be more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're going to a villa in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.04,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,A villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Will the old guy with the glasses complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:05.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't really your father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.20,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi's father was an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Daichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.03,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.47,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,An astronaut?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.34,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.97,Default - italics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,This footage was taken by a local resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.89,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.23,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Come to Izu with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:47.20,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you interested in this avatar's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come, won't you, Daichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.91,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you once the schedule's worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy summer vacation together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.73,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.75,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,The wind in this town feels strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:21.61,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,And the dream I had before I woke \Nup this morning really bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.03,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:32.40,Default - italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And now, an update on the strange light \Nthat appeared over Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:39.97,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, at 11:20 PM, a strange light \Nwas seen shining above Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.67,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The weather bureau says it might \Nhave been either a moonbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.22,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.91,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}a rainbow formed from lunar light,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.32,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.75,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.90,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}or a meteorological phenomenon \Nknown as a circumhorizontal arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.90,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.59,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Baku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:56.42,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really quitting the track team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.06,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I already submitted the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.02,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,That's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.59,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.68,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.07,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you a candidate for the next captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.28,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.80,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.18,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.58,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you ever had a dream \Nyou couldn't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.75,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,one that really bothered you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:26.46,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.40,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:35.55,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams disappear the minute you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:36.98,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.81,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Life is no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.63,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're dead, everything's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:54.81,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since we've \Ngone to a festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.33,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.04,Default - flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Festival? What are they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.12,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.77,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,A festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:46.19,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:59.18,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,Comprehensive Japanese \N— Modern —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.50,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.42,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to study for your make-up tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.25,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I promised someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.27,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I didn't promise anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.30,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stay out too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:41.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Your teachers said to make sure you didn't \Nget into the habit of staying out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.31,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.06,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Have I eaten any watermelon this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.90,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you've had any yet this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.28,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.79,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,What are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.60,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,These memories I've been \Nrecalling in flashes all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.67,Default - flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Festival? What are they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:23.83,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.50,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.24,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some time now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:32.06,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.87,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a photographer for a men's fashion magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:39.91,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in being a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.74,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.93,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky to have run into someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:47.82,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make a great model!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:48.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.18,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.25,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.89,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.43,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know unless you try, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:00.47,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,A future you don't choose doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.35,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Being a model's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.68,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world becomes so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.70,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.67,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've got somewhere to be today, \Nand I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.38,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.27,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.37,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you'd like, you can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:54.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very kind thing to do \Nfor a girl you've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way to a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who was like family to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Like family to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was raised by someone who wasn't my parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.85,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But she wasn't really interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:18.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She was only interested in my inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She raised me to get her hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:26.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And when I realized that, \NI got mad and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:32.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But she died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't forgiven her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.74,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:52.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I use people to survive, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, I'm the same as she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:13:00.17,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Don't people live by helping one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:05.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,My way of life can't be masked \Nby such beautiful words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm living in a way I hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And that makes my heart heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:18.05,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not start by changing the way you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:23.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, that will make your heart lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:38.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.12,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The same as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The bus has been involved in a minor collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:59.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, but all passengers \Nare asked to disembark here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.26,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was in too much of a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.60,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.61,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.38,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I'm amazed you're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.56,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Real people don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, real princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You should go to a hospital, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.39,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... I guess I'll take \Na taxi or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.89,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going the same way, want to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:42.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think I'm going \Nthe same way as you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.82,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, my handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine on Third Street, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There was a bus accident, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.48,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You found out about that fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:10.06,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get that kind of news on the taxi radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:19.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling there'd be a bus \Naccident in this area tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Like, intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:25.57,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No, isn't that like a like psychic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of déjà vu, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:34.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When you visit a place for the first time, \Nbut you feel you've been there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a really strong sense of that all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.59,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Another coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:44.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I even ended up predicting a bus accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's basically psychic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live in a country where \Nthey believe in things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.22,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,A country?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.14,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "a country \Nwhere they believe"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:07.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,if you could relive a day with perfect \Nmemories of what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.33,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:15.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew what would happen, \Nyou could do whatever you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.47,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be boring to \Njust repeat the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:25.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's more exciting not \Nknowing what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel frustrated, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.29,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you haven't forgotten anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.23,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:01.01,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I decide I had to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:05.77,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel like I've forgotten something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.00,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Please let the mission go well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.65,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.02,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What have I forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:25.41,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,I love the view of space \Nfrom this planet most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.45,Default - flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.26,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.44,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:55.87,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But how do I get back, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.28,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,How about a candy apple, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Those look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.71,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.04,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I promised someone I'd eat one with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.64,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,so not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.76,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.11,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.34,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.34,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.52,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:37.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,How much for one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Three shots for two hundred yen! It's a bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,One go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.14,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But you have natural talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.63,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Daichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.34,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The plan's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.51,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving for that villa tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.77,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Another close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.89,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.11,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Real people don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.71,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You guys keep saying that. What's a real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:21.04,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're dead, everything's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.75,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:27.24,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The hopes my father left are still within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.70,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,A future you don't choose doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.83,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to choose one, \Nof my own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.08,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Don't aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.62,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Like the way you don't look at your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.09,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,and think, "This is my right hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:48.19,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Your right hand is a part of you, \Nso it's natural for it to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.89,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like it's me and the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:56.69,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's like both of us comprise "me."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:03.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This shooting game doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:06.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to that villa and do something more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:08.53,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.29,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go to the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:16.62,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to do, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:25.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm going \Nthe same way as you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.31,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.60,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm following the path I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aim carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:53.75,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.16,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What was I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:20.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:22.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:25.49,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:26.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:27.35,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:31.21,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:36.66,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:16.29,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The hyperspace transport Entangle Link
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:20.77,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,carries our ship, {\i1}Blume{\i0}, away from Earth, \Nto a world unexplored by man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:25.51,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But we landed somewhere other than our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:29.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,And the Kiltgang appears there to destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:32.78,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine is in terrible danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.45,0:24:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 24 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:38.16,Title2,D,0000,0000,0000,,Auberon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.11,0:24:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auberon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.16,0:24:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
